<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Minh Shop</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; min-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: #FAFAFA; color: #222222;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div style="background-color: #0070f3; padding: 24px; color: #ffffff;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center;">
                Welcome to @minh</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 24px; background-color: #ffffff;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Hello {{name}},</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Thank you for registering with @minh. To activate your
                account, please click the following link:</p>
            <h2 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center;">
            <a href="http://localhost:9555/v1/api/users/check_email_token?token={{activationToken}}&name={{name}}&date_of_birth={{date_of_birth}}" style="color: #0070f3; text-decoration: none;">Activate your account</a>
            </h2>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Please click this link within the next 5 minutes.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">If you did not register for a @minh account, please
                ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 24px;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact
                us at <a href="https://youtube.com/@minh" target="_blank"
                    style="color: #000; text-decoration:none;">@minh
                </a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body> 
</html>